 <span data-ttu-id="217c2-462">Quando si implementa un metodo che viene identificato come un evento ETW in un <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-classe derivata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="217c2-462">When you implement a method that is identified as an ETW event in an <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-derived class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="217c2-463">È necessario chiamare la classe di base <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> metodo passando la <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A> e gli stessi argomenti come il metodo implementato simile all'esempio seguente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="217c2-463">You must call the base class <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> method passing the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A> and the same arguments as the implemented method similar to the following example.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
